"2:24:12" : {s: 2, a: 24, w: 12, r: "عدد", t: "أُعِدَّتْ", l: "أَعَدَّ", lc: 20, tl: "uʿiddat", lb: "প্রস্তুত করা",e: "prepared", b: "প্রস্তুত করা হয়েছে", i: "disediakan", f: 4, rm: "to count, number, reckon, make the census of. addun - number, computation, determined number. adadun - number. iddatun - a number, prescribed term, counting, to count, legal waiting period for a woman after she is divorced or becomes a widow before she may marry again. add - to prepare, make ready. addina - those who count. madudun - counted one.", ag: "فعل ماض صيغة ٤", eg: "Verb Perfect 4th form", tag: "V", pos: "V", att: "PERF", qual: "(IV)", deg: "3", gen: "F", num: "S", mood: "", lu: "أَعَدَّ"},
